Description:
Secure Entry - Secure Investment
This unit is in the middle of town and it's so easy to walk to the Market, Plaza, shops and train station that you don't need your car.
The kitchen has its own dining area, there is a separate lounge with large glass door opening onto the balcony that overlooks the street and front garden.
There are two large bedrooms and a renovated bathroom.
This group is divided into two smaller buildings, each with separate secure entry and intercom and there is a covered carpark on Title.
Currently let so will make a great investment or buy now and move in when the Lease expires.
INSPECT WITH CONFIDENCE!

Description:
Sold
This well-maintained, first floor apartment offers the kind of low maintenance living that allows plenty of time to enjoy the amenity rich neighbourhood. Positioned walking distance to Hemmings Park, Greaves Reserve, Dandenong Hospital, the vibrant Dandenong Markets and Plaza as well as easy transport options with Dandenong Train Station, Princes Highway, Eastlink and the Monash Freeway all close by.
The functional layout includes an open kitchen and meals area, separate living room, two large bedrooms with built in robes with mirrors and a renovated bathroom with space for laundry facilities. A central reverse cycle air conditioner provides indoor comfort and a car space and open yard complete the maintenance free exterior.
Spacious interiors, first floor security and a brilliant location with everything you need just around the corner; this apartment is a fantastic purchasing opportunity perfect for first home buyers, investors and downsizers alike.
• First floor apartment in the heart of Dandenong
• Open kitchen and meals area, separate living room and two robed bedrooms
• Renovated bathroom with large shower and laundry facilities
• Quiet position in the centre of the block plus off street parking space and an open yard
• Great location walking distance to schools, parks, shops and convenient access to transport options

Description:
NEAR NEW MODERN LIVING
Located within the highly sought after Central Dandenong, moments from shopping centres, a selection of primary and secondary schools including Dandenong South Primary School, local sporting facilities, transport links and freeway access, this near new townhouse has it all! Enjoy picturesque surroundings at your doorstep whilst strolling through parklands and wetlands creating a highly desirable environment for any astute buyer.
Ground Floor:
This impressive design townhouse consist of two separate living areas, a contemporary kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, ample cupboard and island bench perfect for the aspiring chef. The kitchen overlooks the open plan family/dining area with porcelain tiles throughout leading out to the private courtyard ideal for all-year-round entertaining. A remote controlled single garage with internal access plus an easy care private courtyard with handyman shed.
Upstairs:
Compromising three spacious bedrooms with built in robes, great size main bedroom with built in robes and modern en-suite with double vanities and shower. The other two bedrooms serviced by a generous sized bathroom with oversized vanity, ceramic bath and shower.
EXTRA FEATURES INCLUDE:
Porcelain Tiles throughout upstairs open living area.
Remote controlled single garage with internal access.
* Ample cupboard space throughout the home.
* Fully landscaped front and rear gardens.
* Central heating and cooling for perfect climate control.
* Within minutes of Bus services, Dandenong Train Station, Dandenong Plaza and Eastlink
This near new townhouse showcases ultra-modern fixtures and contemporary interiors promising to compliment all d?cor.

When Style and Convenience Meet

Offering comfort, style and set upon 3 levels, the unique property incorporates 3 bedrooms including master bedroom with full en suite and sweeping views towards Dandenong, open plan living which features a focal kitchen between the lounge and dining areas, 2 balconies highlighted by magnificent views of the CBD and surrounds, single lock up garage with remote entrance and direct internal access as well as additional off street car space, a total of 3 bathrooms and 3 toilets and an array of inclusions such as Daikin split system air conditioning, carpets and tiles throughout, ample storage and bench space in kitchen as well as gas cook top and all stainless steel appliances. The home is ideal for family living but also for young couples or first home buyers who do not want lots of maintenance and is only 1 year old meaning that it is covered under builder structural warranty. Description:
Young, modern and affordable.
Quality meets affordability in this impressive, low maintenance modern family home positioned in the popular Meridian Estate in Dandenong. A fine first home, a strong investment or a perfect downsize. Open plan living/ dining space,outdoor entertaining areas plus an additonal formal living room are complemented by 3 spacious bedrooms including master with an ensuite and main bathroom with separate toilet.
Internally, the home offers immediate appeal with large gas kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, modern glass splashback, dishwasher and an abundance of cupboard space.
Ensuring year round comfort, the home features central ducted heating and evaporative cooling alongside other features such as l.e.d downlights, 2.5kw solar panels, large garden shed and single lock up garage with dual access.
Central and convenient, this highly popular location is a short walk to local schools such as Dandenong South Primary School all while being within close proximity to Dandenong train station, Eastlink and everything central Dandenong has to offer.

Description:
A private and quietly positioned 2 bedroom rear unit
A well maintained and looked after unit just south of central Dandenong. An ideal home if you are looking to downsize, add to your investment portfolio or a great first home. As you enter the home you are welcomed by a large lounge with the comfort of split system air conditioner. Separate Modern kitchen with gas cooking and lots of storage which leads into the very spacious meals area. There are 2 bedrooms that both feature built in wardrobes as well as a family bathroom tiled from floor to ceiling and a separate toilet. Outside you find a single garage plus room to park additional cars.
Ducted heating throughout the house for your comfort complete the picture.
Outside you find a massive courtyard which is ideal for entertaining and hosting your parties.
Easy access to buses, Dandenong train station, Dandenong South Primary School, kindergarten, all major arterial roads and all of central Dandenong's facilities just minutes away.
